<HEADLINE>
FT  25 OCT 94 / People: Non-executive directors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rhidian Brynmor Jones has resigned from SERCO GROUP.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Serco Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
