<TEXT>
Stephen Barraclough, chief financial officer at News International for the
past three years, is leaving to take up a similar post with EMI Music
worldwide. His new job takes him and his family back to New York, where he
was working as US finance and marketing director for Marks &amp; Spencer before
joining News International.
