report to the president and ceo, James Fifield, who says Barraclough 'will
play a significant part in the achievement of our long-term strategies'.
According to News International, Barraclough, 42, has 'done an outstanding
job of restructuring our financial operations and introducing more
sophisticated planning and control procedures throughout the business'.
