</XX>
<IN>P7999 Amusement and Recreation, NEC.
    P7011 Hotels and Motels.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
    TECH  Safety &amp; Standards.
    TECH  Services &amp; Services use.
</TP>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
