<HEADLINE>
FT  24 OCT 94 / 'Keen interest' in Coal Products
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
More than 10 companies have indicated an interest in buying Coal Products,
British Coal's solid smokeless fuel subsidiary. Mr Ray Proctor, British
Coal's finance director, said: 'We are very pleased at the keen interest
shown.'
Coal Products is British Coal's biggest subsidiary, with 30 per cent of the
smokeless fuel market.
